-for-rosseler-at-garmin-sharp|title=No contract for Rosseler at Garmin-Sharp|work=[[Cyclingnews.com]]|publisher=[[Future plc]]|location=[[Bath, Somerset|Bath]], [[England]]|date=5 October 2013|accessdate=5 October 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nieuwsblad.be/sportwereld/cnt/dmf20131004_00776062|language=Dutch|title=Rosseler moet weg bij Garmin-Sharp|trans-title=Rosseler leaves Garmin-Sharp|work=[[Het Nieuwsblad]]|publisher=[[Corelio]]|location=[[Antwerp]], [[Flanders]]|date=5 October 2013|accessdate=24 October 2013}}</ref> Born in [[Verviers]], [[Wallonia]], Belgium, Rosseler currently resides in [[Tongeren]], [[Flanders]], Belgium.<ref name=\"2014team\">{{cite news|url=http://veranclassic-doltcini.be/rosseler.html|title=S\u00e9bastien Rosseler at Veranclassic\u2013Doltcini|date=21 January 2014|access-date=6 January 2014|work=Veranclassic\u2013Doltcini|publisher=Geoffrey Coup\u00e9|location=[[Jemappes]], [[Walloon Region|Walloon]]|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222143703/http://veranclassic-doltcini.be/rosseler.html|archive-date=22 February 2014|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n==Career achievements==\n===Major results===\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n;2002\n: 1st [[File:Jersey yellow.svg|20px]] Overall [[Le Triptyque des Monts et Ch\u00e2teaux]]\n;2003\n: 1st [[File:Jersey yellow.svg|20px]] Overall [[Le Triptyque des Monts et Ch\u00e2teaux]]\n: [[Olympia's Tour]]\n::1st [[File:Jersey green.svg|20px|Green jersey]] Points classification\n::1st Stages 1, 6 & 7 ([[Individual time trial|ITT]])\n: 6th [[De Vlaamse Pijl]]\n;2004\n: 8th Overall [[Four Days of Dunkirk]]\n: 9th [[2006 Gent\u2013Wevelgem|Gent\u2013Wevelgem]]\n;2006\n: 2nd Overall [[Tour of Belgium]]\n: 3rd [[Halle\u2013Ingooigem]]\n: 4th Overall [[Three Days of De Panne]]\n: 7th Overall [[Four Days of Dunkirk]]\n::1st [[File:Jersey white.svg|20px|White jersey]] Young rider classification\n;2007\n: 1st Stage 1 ([[Team time trial|TTT]]) [[2007 Tour of Qatar|Tour of Qatar]]\n: 4th O